definition: Anji county in Huzhou 湖州[Hu2 zhou1], Zhejiang
content/calm/still/quiet/safe/secure/in good health/to find a place for/to install/to fix/to fit/to bring (a charge against sb)/to pacify/to harbor (good intentions)/security/safety/peace/ampere
surname Ji/abbr. for Jilin Province 吉林省[Ji2 lin2 Sheng3]

sentences.english: Bacterial needle blight has became an epidemic of Chinese fir forests in Anji County in recent years.
sentences.chinese: 杉木細菌性葉枯病近幾年在安吉縣大量流行。

sentences.english: It also has China's largest bamboo nursery.
sentences.chinese: 安吉縣同時也是中國最大的竹苗圃。

sentences.english: Anji County in Zhejiang province is one of ten famous bamboo home in China.
sentences.chinese: 浙江省安吉縣爲我國十大“竹鄉”之一。

sentences.english: Tianhuangping pumped storage power station is located in Anji County, Zhejiang Province.
sentences.chinese: 天荒坪抽水蓄能電站位於浙江省安吉縣。

sentences.english: Bamboo snout moth is the main bamboo insect in Anji county, Zhejiang province.
sentences.chinese: 竹螟是浙江省安吉縣的竹子主要害蟲。
